bill.longTitleEn: Bill entitled an Act to reduce restrictions on the power of the Electricity Supply Board to carry out works concerning the levels on the Shannon Lakes (Lough Derg, Lough Ree and Lough Allen), to amend the Electricity (Supply) (Amendment) (No. 2) Act 1934 and to provide for related matters.
bill.longTitleGa: Bille dá ngairtear Acht do laghdú srianta ar chumhacht Bhord Soláthair an Leictreachais oibreacha a dhéanamh maidir leis na leibhéil ar Lochanna na Sionainne (Loch Deirgeirt, Loch Rí agus Loch Aillionn), do leasú an Achta Leictreachais (Soláthar) (Leasú) (Uimh. 2), 1934 agus do dhéanamh socrú i dtaobh nithe gaolmhara.

debates.showAs: Health (Postponement of Certain Leave) Bill 2024: First Stage

bill.longTitleEn: Bill entitled an Act to amend and extend the Maternity Protection Act 1994 and the Adoptive Leave Act 1995 and for those purposes to provide a mechanism to postpone maternity leave or adoptive leave in circumstances where a person is diagnosed with or being treated for cancer and to provide for related matters.
bill.longTitleGa: Bille dá ngairtear Acht do leasú agus do leathnú an Achta um Chosaint Mháithreachais, 1994 agus an Achta um Shaoire Uchtaíoch, 1995 agus chun na gcríoch sin do sholáthar sásra chun saoire mháithreachais nó saoire uchtaíoch a iarchur in imthosca ina bhfáthmheastar go bhfuil ailse ar dhuine nó ina bhfuil cóireáil in aghaidh ailse á cur ar dhuine agus do dhéanamh socrú i dtaobh nithe gaolmhara.
bill.shortTitleGa: An Bille Sláinte (Saoire Áirithe a Iarchur), 2024

debates.showAs: Horticultural Peat (Temporary Measures) Bill 2021: Second Stage
Horticultural Peat (Temporary Measures) Bill 2021: First Stage

bill.longTitleEn: Bill entitled an Act to amend the Planning and Development Acts 2000 to 2021 and the Environmental Protection Agency Acts 1992 to 2011 to make exceptional provision for peat extraction for the purpose of horticulture for a temporary period in the public interest in order to mitigate the adverse consequences resulting, or likely to result from an interruption to supply and to provide for a just transition.
bill.longTitleGa: Bille dá ngairtear Acht do leasú na nAchtanna um Pleanáil agus Forbairt, 2000 go 2021 agus na nAchtanna fán nGníomhaireacht um Chaomhnú Comhshaoil, 1992 go 2011 chun socrú eisceachtúil a dhéanamh maidir le baint móna chun críche gairneoireachta ar feadh tréimhse shealadach ar mhaithe le leas an phobail d’fhonn maolú a dhéanamh ar na hiarmhairtí dochracha a bheidh, nó is dóigh a bheidh, mar thoradh ar bhriseadh ar sholáthar agus do dhéanamh socrú maidir le trasdul cóir.
bill.shortTitleGa: An Bille um Móin Ghairneoireachta (Bearta Sealadacha), 2021

bill.longTitleEn: Bill entitled an Act to confirm that the choral refrain, with or without the lyrics, of  "Amhrán na bhFiann" or, in the English Language, "The Soldier's Song" is and continues to be the National Anthem; to provide for a version of the National Anthem in the Irish Sign Language;  to confirm that the Presidential Salute is and continues to be the music of the first 4 bars, followed by the last 4 bars, of the National Anthem; and to provide for other related matters.
bill.longTitleGa: Bille dá ngairtear Acht do dhaingniú gurb é an loinneog chórúil "Amhrán na bhFiann" nó, sa Bhéarla, "The Soldier's Song", leis na liricí nó gan iad, an Rosc Náisiúnta agus go leanann sé de bheith mar an Rosc Náisiúnta; do dhéanamh socrú maidir le leagan den Rosc Náisiúnta i dTeanga Chomharthaíochta na hÉireann; do dhaingniú gurb é ceol na chéad 4 bharra den Rosc Náisiúnta agus ceol na 4 bharra deiridh de ina dhiaidh Cúirtéis an Uachtaráin agus go leanann sé de bheith mar Chúirtéis an Uachtaráin; agus do dhéanamh socrú i dtaobh nithe gaolmhara eile.
bill.shortTitleGa: An Bille um an Rosc Náisiúnta, 2019

debates.showAs: Farm Safety Agency Bill 2018: Second Stage
Farm Safety Agency Bill 2018: First Stage

bill.longTitleEn: Bill entitled an Act to provide for the establishment of a body to be known as an Ghníomhaireacht um Shábháilteacht Feirme or in the English language as the Farm Safety Agency; to define its functions and its role within the Health and Safety Authority and for those purposes to amend the Safety, Health and Welfare at Work Act 2005; and to provide for related matters.
bill.longTitleGa: Bille dá ngairtear Acht do dhéanamh socrú maidir le comhlacht a bhunú ar a dtabharfar an Ghníomhaireacht um Shábháilteacht Feirme nó, sa Bhéarla, the Farm Safety Agency; do mhíniú a fheidhmeanna agus a róil laistigh den Údarás Sláinte agus Sábháilteachta agus, chun na gcríoch sin, do leasú an Achta um Shábháilteacht, Sláinte agus Leas ag an Obair, 2005; agus do dhéanamh socrú i dtaobh nithe gaolmhara.
bill.shortTitleGa: An Bille fán nGníomhaireacht um Shábháilteacht Feirme, 2018

debates.showAs: Life Saving Equipment Bill 2017: Committee Stage
Life Saving Equipment Bill 2017: Restoration to Order Paper
Life Saving Equipment Bill 2017: Second Stage
Life Saving Equipment Bill 2017: First Stage

bill.longTitleEn: Bill entitled an Act to provide for a specific offence of interfering with Life Saving Equipment and to provide for related matters.
bill.longTitleGa: Bille dá ngairtear Acht do dhéanamh socrú maidir le cion sonrach arb éard é cur isteach ar threalamh tarrthála beatha agus do dhéanamh socrú i dtaobh nithe gaolmhara.
bill.shortTitleGa: An Bille um Threalamh Tarrthála Beatha, 2017

Declaration of Independence Day Bill 2017: Committee Stage
Declaration of Independence Day Bill 2017: Second Stage
Declaration of Independence Day Bill 2017: Second Stage (Resumed)
Declaration of Independence Day Bill 2017: First Stage

bill.longTitleEn: Bill entitled an Act to recognise the meeting of the First Dáil and the Declaration of Independence made on 21 January 1919 and to provide for a "Declaration of Independence Day" to be held on 21 January annually and to provide for related matters
bill.longTitleGa: Bille dá ngairtear Acht d'aithint thionól na Chéad Dála agus na Faisnéise Neamhspleáchais a rinneadh an 21 Eanáir 1919 agus do dhéanamh socrú maidir le "Lá na Faisnéise Neamhspleáchais" a thionólfar an 21 Eanáir gach bliain agus do dhéanamh socrú i dtaobh nithe gaolmhara
bill.shortTitleGa: An Bille um Lá na Faisnéise Neamhspleáchais 2017
